               <p>Third London Jury, before John Mirehouse, Esquire.</p>
               <p>1129. 
               
                  <persName id="t18330704-107-defend1056" type="defendantName">
                     THOMAS 
                     HOBLEY
                  <interp inst="t18330704-107-defend1056" type="surname" value="HOBLEY"></interp>
